    "features" : { "type" : "div",  "id" : "veincaller-features",               "content" : [
        { "type" : "h1",            "className" : "titleHeader",                "content" : "Veincaller" },
        "Veincallers are the most mysterious and misunderstood type of Vampire, for their connection to blood goes beyond the physical. Unlike other Vampires, Veincallers cultivate dark magic with your blood before it even leaves your veins.",
        { "type" : "div",           "className" : "feature-container",    "content" :[
            { "type" : "div",       "className" : "feature-header",       "content" : "Level 3: Spellcasting" },
            "You have learned to use the blood you steal to invoke spells.",
            { "type" : "div",       "className" : "indent",                     "content" : [
                { "type" : "span",  "className" : "text-label",                 "content" : "Cantrips. " },
                "You know two cantrips of your choice from the Vampire spell list. Whenever you gain a Vampire level, you can replace one of these cantrips with another cantrip of your choice from the Vampire spell list.",
                { "type" : "div",   "className" : "indent",                     "content" : "When you reach Vampire level 10, you learn another Veincaller cantrip of your choice."}
            ]},
            { "type" : "div",       "className" : "indent",                     "content" : [
                { "type" : "span",  "className" : "text-label",                 "content" : "Spell Slots. " },
                "The Veincaller Spellcasting table shows how many spell slots you have to cst your level 1+ spells. You regain all expended spell slots when you finish a Long Rest."
            ]},
            { "type" : "div",       "className" : "indent",                     "content" : [
                { "type" : "span",  "className" : "text-label",                 "content" : "Prepared Spells of Level 1+. " },
                "You prepare the list of level 1+ spells that are available to you to cast with this feature. To start, choose three level 1 spells from the Vampire spell list.",
                { "type" : "div",   "className" : "indent",                     "content" : "The number of spells on your list increases as you gain Vampire levels, as shown in the Prepared Spells column of the Veincaller Spellcasting table. Whenever that number increases, choose additional spells from the Vampire spell list until the number of spells from the Vampire spell list matches the number on the table. The chosen spells must be of a level for which you have spell slots."}
            ]},
            { "type" : "div",       "className" : "indent",                     "content" : [
                { "type" : "span",  "className" : "text-label",                 "content" : "Changing Your Prepared Spells. " },
                "Whenever you gain a Vampire level, you can replace one spell on your list with another Vampire spell for which you have spell slots."
            ]},
            { "type" : "div",       "className" : "indent",                     "content" : [
                { "type" : "span",  "className" : "text-label",                 "content" : "Spellcasting Ability. " },
                "Charisma is your spellcasting ability for your Vampire spells."
            ]},
            { "type" : "div",       "className" : "indent",                     "content" : [
